Class ThymeleafTag

java.lang.Object
jakarta.servlet.jsp.tagext.TagSupport
jakarta.servlet.jsp.tagext.BodyTagSupport
com.foreach.across.modules.web.jsp.ThymeleafTag
All Implemented Interfaces:
jakarta.servlet.jsp.tagext.BodyTag, jakarta.servlet.jsp.tagext.IterationTag, jakarta.servlet.jsp.tagext.JspTag, jakarta.servlet.jsp.tagext.Tag, Serializable
public class ThymeleafTag extends jakarta.servlet.jsp.tagext.BodyTagSupport

Simple tag that allows rendering a Thymeleaf template from a JSP. Requires Thymeleaf support to be enabled and servlet-api to be present.

Based on source code from org.thymeleaf.spring4.view.ThymeleafView

.
Author:
Arne Vandamme
